## Description
* There are sites and communities who specialize in listing or promoting products being invented
* You can designate your proposal to make it clear that it is not a product yet, but one under develeopment

## Tips
* Your use of this depends on how complete a product concept you have
* The expectation is that the description is quite polished
* Be careful about the sites terms and conditions so you don't mislead audience into thinking they can invest in or buy the product yet

